  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators conducted a pilot study to compare the effect of Positive End Expiratory
      Pressure(PEEP) setting guide by the highest on oxygenation and by lung electrical impedance
      tomography(EIT) on survival in subjects with severe Acute Respiratory Distress
      Syndrome(ARDS).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
